  "keyFeatures": [
    "HEALPix-based spatial gridding with equal-area cells",
    "Split-Apply-Combine workflow for large-scale data processing",
    "Sidecar pattern for non-destructive data indexing",
    "Streaming accumulation for incremental data ingestion",
    "GeoParquet integration for modern geospatial workflows",
    "Robust statistics (MAD, robust_std) for outlier handling",
    "Both Python API and CLI tools",
    "Optimized for planetary science and sparse observation datasets"
